ey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wembley\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the equivalent\", \"from\": 1033, \"to\": 1047}, {\"ngram\": \"nearly 29 Olympic swimming pools\", \"from\": 1051, \"to\": 1083}, {\"ngram\": \"more than three times the length\", \"from\": 1088, \"to\": 1120}, {\"ngram\": \"the pitch\", \"from\": 1124, \"to\": 1133}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It could mean part of the road will reopen next week as early as Wednesday when the rest of the water has been removed,BBC Newsreported.\", \"from\": 1147, \"to\": 1283, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 1161, \"to\": 1165}, {\"ngram\": \"the road\", \"from\": 1169, \"to\": 1177}, {\"ngram\": \"Wednesday\", \"from\": 1212, \"to\": 1221}, {\"ngram\": \"the rest\", \"from\": 1227, \"to\": 1235}, {\"ngram\": \"the water\", \"from\": 1239, \"to\": 1248}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But major repairs could be required, with at least one slip road needing to be resurfaced, further delaying its reopening,Bedford Independentreported.\", \"from\": 1285, \"to\": 1435, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"major repairs\", \"from\": 1289, \"to\": 1302}, {\"ngram\": \"at least one slip road\", \"from\": 1327, \"to\": 1349}, {\"ngram\": \"its reopening\", \"from\": 1393, \"to\": 1406}, {\"ngram\": \"Bedford\", \"from\": 1407, \"to\": 1414}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mr Fellows said: 'We will be working around the clock to carry out repairs and get the road reopened as soon as it is safe to do so.\", \"from\": 1437, \"to\": 1569, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Mr Fellows\", \"from\": 1437, \"to\": 1447}, {\"ngram\": \"the clock\", \"from\": 1481, \"to\": 1490}, {\"ngram\": \"repairs\", \"from\": 1504, \"to\": 1511}, {\"ngram\": \"the road\", \"from\": 1520, \"to\": 1528}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'It may be possible to open some elements of the road towards the end of next week - such as one lane in each direction - but we will only do that when we are certain it's safe.'\", \"from\": 1571, \"to\": 1749, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some elements\", \"from\": 1599, \"to\": 1612}, {\"ngram\": \"the road\", \"from\": 1616, \"to\": 1624}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 1633, \"to\": 1640}, {\"ngram\": \"next week\", \"from\": 1644, \"to\": 1653}, {\"ngram\": \"one lane\", \"from\": 1664, \"to\": 1672}, {\"ngram\": \"each direction\", \"from\": 1676, \"to\": 1690}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There is anger that this happened in the first place, after the pumping station tasked with removing floodwater was itself flooded.\", \"from\": 1751, \"to\": 1882, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"anger\", \"from\": 1760, \"to\": 1765}, {\"ngram\": \"the first place\", \"from\": 1788, \"to\": 1803}, {\"ngram\": \"the pumping station\", \"from\": 1811, \"to\": 1830}, {\"ngram\": \"floodwater\", \"from\": 1852, \"to\": 1862}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sue Clark, a Conservative on Central Bedfordshire Council, said: 'Nobody can think of it as anything other than a national disgrace.\", \"from\": 1884, \"to\": 2016, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1884, \"end\": 1887, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sue_Sylvester\", \"score\": 0.8921162232117812, \"rank\": 0.11746483047850807, \"text\": \"Sue\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sue_Sylvester\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sue_Sylvester\"}, {\"begin\": 1913, \"end\": 1941, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Central_Bedfordshire_Council\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Central Bedfordshire Council\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q11204\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Central_Bedfordshire_Council\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Central_Bedfordshire_Council\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a Conservative\", \"from\": 1895, \"to\": 1909}, {\"ngram\": \"Nobody\", \"from\": 1950, \"to\": 1956}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 1976, \"to